data.title: Montagu Sherard Dawes Butler
data.meta_description: Sir Montagu Sherard Dawes Butler, was Governor of the Central Provinces of British India (1925–33), Lieutenant Governor of the Isle of Man (1933–37), and Master of Pembroke College, Cambridge (1937–48).
